title: Spinning top, puppet among 12 Toy Hall of Fame finalists - Chico Enterprise-Record
text:
The spinning top, coloring book, Wiffle Ball and puppet are vying for a place in the National Toy Hall of Fame. The simple classics are among 12 finalists for this year's class announced Monday.
 Chico Enterprise-Record.
